herrie (1.1-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Bump to 1.1: Lots of cleanups, but also some improvements:
    - Pause/skip songs with SIGUSR1 and SIGUSR2
    - Percentages with vertical progress (like Mutt)
    - Improved handling of symlinks

 -- Ed Schouten <ed@fxq.nl>  Sun, 22 Dec 2006 14:30:00 +0100

herrie (1.0.2-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Bump to 1.0.2: Adds new features and small performance improvements:
    - Add ^W and ^U button to remove words and sentences.
    - Add 'c' button to easily change directories.
    - Speed up randomizing.

 -- Ed Schouten <ed@fxq.nl>  Sun, 10 Dec 2006 12:00:00 +0100

herrie (1.0.1-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Bump to 1.0.1: Improves Ogg Vorbis tag support.

 -- Ed Schouten <ed@fxq.nl>  Sun, 3 Dec 2006 14:00:00 +0100

